    "explainability": "very_high",
    "explanation": "This signal identifies page-level content that is suitable for family audiences and compliant with children's privacy laws. Content is classified based on publisher declarations, content rating systems (G, TV-Y, E), and automated + human content analysis. NO user data is collected or used. NO behavioral tracking occurs. NO persistent identifiers are placed on devices for users under 13. Targeting is purely contextual based on content suitability. All placements are age-gated to prevent inappropriate exposure. Parents maintain full control through age verification screens.",
